/*
Space templates

Styleguide 7.0
*/
.space-template__dialog
  padding: 0
  .title
    margin: 0

/*
Space template list

A module which contains a list of icons and labels for Space Templates
with a detail view on the right

Markup:
div(class="space-template__dialog" style="width: 700px; height: 600px;")
  div(class="space-template__list")
    div(class="space-template__item")
      img(class="space-template__icon")
      p(class="space-template__label") Template name
    div(class="space-template__item")
      img(class="space-template__icon")
      p(class="space-template__label") Template name
  div(class="space-template__detail")
    div(class="space-template__detail-content")
      h1 Template name
      p Sleep on keyboard. Chase mice leave hair everywhere sleep in the bathroom sink hate dog, and peer out window, chatter at birds, lure them to mouth so ears back wide eyed shove bum in owner's face like camera lens. Play time. Flop over. Run in circles. Always hungry stick butt in face, and hunt by meowing loudly at 5am next to human slave food dispenser but peer out window, chatter at birds, lure them to mouth find empty spot in cupboard and sleep all day. Sun bathe claw drapes have secret plans give attitude hate dog always hungry. Chase dog then run away always hungry, for inspect anything brought into the house lick butt, but intently stare at the same spot. Give attitude curl into a furry donut. Stick butt in face scratch the furniture chase imaginary bugs all of a sudden cat goes crazy loves cheeseburgers bathe private parts with tongue then lick owner's face but sleep nap. Nap all day cat snacks, for attack feet, for give attitude, and attack feet, but have secret plans need to chase tail.

Styleguide 7.1
*/
.space-template__dialog-content
  $display-flexbox()
  position: relative
  height: 600px
  width: 900px
  &.dialog-content
    margin: 0
  > .loading
    margin: auto

.space-template__list,
.space-template__detail
  font-size: 1.1em
  padding-top: 20px
  padding-bottom: 20px

.space-template__list
  width: 70%
.space-template__detail
  width: 30%
  padding-left: 30px
  padding-right: 30px
  background-color: $gray-lighter

.space-template__list,
.space-template__detail-content
  overflow-y: auto

.space-template__detail-content
  height: 498px
  margin-bottom: 10px
  h1
    font-size: 1.3em
    margin-bottom: 25px
  > div, > p
    line-height: 1.4em

.space-template__item
  float: left
  width: 140px
  height: 190px
  text-align: center

.space-template--item-selected
  .space-template__icon
    box-shadow: 0px 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), 1px 1px 1px transparentify($metallic-gray-blueish, 0.4) inset, -1px -1px 1px transparentify($metallic-gray-blueish, 0.4) inset

.space-template__icon
  $display-flexbox()
  align-items: center
  width: 100px
  height: 135px
  margin: 0 auto 8px
  border: 1px solid $metallic-gray-blueish
  border-radius: 2px
  box-shadow: 0px 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)
  img
    margin: auto
  .fa-plus-circle
    margin: auto
    font-size: 50px
    color: $metallic-gray-blueish
  &:hover
    border-color: $blue-link
    box-shadow: 0px 1px 1px transparentify($blue-link, 0.3)

.space-template__contact
  position: absolute
  bottom: 0
  left: 0
  right: 30%
  text-align: center
  padding: 5px

.space-template__space-creation
  width: 100%
  padding: 10px 20px 0px
  .knowledge-base-icon
    font-size: 0.7em
    margin-left: 4px

.space-template__space-creation-form
  width: 50%
  height: 50%
  margin: 10% auto 0
  .l-form
    margin-left: 0
  .dropdown-toggle
    width: 100%
  .buttons
    border: none
/*
Space Template Queue

A view which shows a queue of actions performed when creating space
template items, with variations of success and error for each item

Markup:
div(class="space-template__dialog" style="width: 700px; height: 600px;")
  div(class="space-template__queue")
    h1 Creating template entities
    div(class="space-template__queue-item space-template--item-success") Content Type
    div(class="space-template__queue-item space-template--item-error") Content Type
      span Failed
    div(class="space-template__queue-status") Failed

Styleguide 7.2
*/
.space-template__queue
  width: 100%
  padding: 0px 20px
  margin-top: 10px

.space-template__queue-container
  height: 420px
  overflow-y: auto

.space-template__queue-item
  padding: 4px 0px
  .fa
    margin-right: 4px

.space-template__item-status
  margin-left: 4px

.space-template--item-success
  .fa
    color: $green
.space-template--item-error
  .fa,
  .space-template__item-status
    color: $red

.space-template__queue-status
  font-size: 1.1em
  margin: 10px 0px


.space-template__post-dialog-bg
  $stretch()
  background-color: transparent
  $layer('modalBackground')

.space-template__post-dialog
  position: absolute
  top: 160px
  right: 380px
  width: 450px
  padding: 10px 20px
  border: 1px solid $metallic-gray-blueish
  border-radius: 2px
  box-shadow: 0px 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)
  background-color: transparentify($gray-lightest, 0.9)
  $layer('modalDialog')
  > h2, p
    text-align: center


.space-template__tips-list
  margin-left: 0
  li
    overflow: hidden
    vertical-align: middle
    height: 60px
    margin-bottom: 10px
  .numbered-tooltip__label, p
    float: left
  .numbered-tooltip__label
    margin-right: 10px
  .numbered-tooltip__description
    $display-flexbox()
    flex-direction: column
    justify-content: center
    height: 100%
  p
    font-size: 1.1em
    line-height: 1.2em
    width: 85%
    margin: auto 0

